{"tha-ap168:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap168:0.2":"Suparicariyavagga ","tha-ap168:0.3":"Sappidayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap168:1.1":"“Phusso namasi bhagava, ","tha-ap168:1.2":"ahutinam patiggaho; ","tha-ap168:1.3":"Gacchate vithiyam viro, ","tha-ap168:1.4":"nibbapento mahajanam. ","tha-ap168:2.1":"Anupubbena bhagava, ","tha-ap168:2.2":"agacchi mama santikam; ","tha-ap168:2.3":"Tato tam pattam paggayha, ","tha-ap168:2.4":"sappitelamadasaham. ","tha-ap168:3.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap168:3.2":"yam sappimadadim tada; ","tha-ap168:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap168:3.4":"sappidanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap168:4.1":"Chappannase ito kappe, ","tha-ap168:4.2":"eko asi samodako; ","tha-ap168:4.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap168:4.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap168:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap168:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap168:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap168:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sappidayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap168:7.1":"Sappidayakattherassapadanam chattham. "}